Detailed Description

template<class BPQNode>
class GBPQueue2ConstCursor< BPQNode >

Bounded Priority Queue Cursor. Traverse the queue in descending order. It is NOT safe to detach queue items during the cursor is active because the cursor make a copy of current key.
